result::Result::<T, E>::unwrap_or_else.doc:
Returns the contained [`Ok`] value or computes it from a closure.


# Examples

```
fn count(x: &str) -> usize { x.len() }

assert_eq!(Ok(2).unwrap_or_else(count), 2);
assert_eq!(Err("foo").unwrap_or_else(count), 3);
```

